== Quick Copy Citations

=== BibTeX (Zotero Compatible)

[source,bibtex]
----
@software{{{PROJECT_SLUG}}_{{YEAR}},
  author = {Jewell, Jonathan D.A.},
  title = {{PROJECT_NAME}},
  year = {{YEAR}},
  version = {{{VERSION}}},
  url = {https://github.com/hyperpolymath/{{PROJECT_NAME}}},
  license = {AGPL-3.0-or-later},
  note = {RSR-compliant software}
}
----

